data.enText: a small creature like an insect with six legs, two front claws (= curved and pointed arms) and a long tail that curves over its back and can give a poisonous sting. Scorpions live in hot countries.

tr: arachnid of warm dry regions having a long segmented tail ending in a venomous stinger

value.def: A scorpion is a small creature which looks like a large insect. Scorpions have a long curved tail, and some of them are poisonous.
